name: PismoTides
0:
”Alexa, ask Pismo Tides for help”
”Ask Pismo tides tomorrow”
”Ask Pismo tides saturday”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pismo tides
des: Pismo Tides can tell you the tides for Pismo beach, Oceano dunes for any date past or present. Providing a date for the skill is extremely flexible. For example, invoke the skill with: Ask Pismo tides the tides for tomorrow, this Saturday, next Tuesday or December twenty fifth. Tide information is provided by NOAA / National Ocean Service.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
